PLEASE JUST GO TALK TO HIM.

01:19.705 --> 01:21.164
FOR ME.

01:26.336 --> 01:29.297
PANCREATIC CANCER.

01:29.297 --> 01:31.508
DOCTORS SAID WE'RE

01:29.297 --> 01:31.508
OUT OF OPTIONS AND

01:29.297 --> 01:31.508
I COULD TAKE HIM HOME,

01:31.508 --> 01:32.593
SO THAT'S WHAT I DID.

01:32.593 --> 01:34.386
OH, I'M SORRY.

01:34.386 --> 01:36.931
AGENT HAGEN SAYS

01:34.386 --> 01:36.931
YOU'RE A PROFILER

01:36.931 --> 01:40.017
WHO'S HELPED THE FBI

01:36.931 --> 01:40.017
SOLVE IMPOSSIBLE CASES.

01:40.017 --> 01:42.519
I TAKE IT YOU GOT ONE

01:40.017 --> 01:42.519
INVOLVING YOUR FATHER.

01:42.519 --> 01:45.898
MY DAD WAS AN FBI AGENT HERE

01:42.519 --> 01:45.898
IN PORTLAND FOR OVER 40 YEARS.

01:45.898 --> 01:48.191
HE TOOK A LOT OF BAD GUYS

01:45.898 --> 01:48.191
OFF THE STREETS,

01:48.191 --> 01:50.861
BUT NONE OF THAT

01:48.191 --> 01:50.861
IS GONNA END UP IN HIS OBITUARY

01:50.861 --> 01:52.905
BECAUSE OF THE ONE

01:50.861 --> 01:52.905
THAT GOT AWAY.

01:52.905 --> 01:56.283
BEFORE MY FATHER DIES,

01:52.905 --> 01:56.283
HELP ME DO ONE THING FOR HIM.

01:56.283 --> 01:58.869
HELP ME BRING

01:56.283 --> 01:58.869
D.B. COOPER TO JUSTICE.

01:58.869 --> 01:59.954
WAIT.

01:59.954 --> 02:01.204
THE NUMBER-ONE UNSOLVED MYSTERY

02:01.204 --> 02:02.581
IN THE HISTORY

02:01.204 --> 02:02.581
OF AMERICAN CRIME --

02:02.581 --> 02:04.124
THAT'S OUR NEW JOB?

02:04.124 --> 02:06.460
NO, OUR JOB IS TO TAKE DOWN

02:04.124 --> 02:06.460
OLIVER SCHMIDT.

02:06.460 --> 02:08.211
THIS IS JUST A DETOUR.

02:06.460 --> 02:08.211
SOPHIE?

02:08.211 --> 02:11.256
IT'S 1971,

02:08.211 --> 02:11.256
THE DAY BEFORE THANKSGIVING.

02:11.256 --> 02:14.969
A 727 TAKES OFF FROM PORTLAND

02:11.256 --> 02:14.969
BOUND FOR SEATTLE.

02:14.969 --> 02:16.971
IT IS HIJACKED BY THIS MAN,

02:16.971 --> 02:20.140
A PASSENGER WHO GOES BY THE NAME

02:16.971 --> 02:20.140
OF DAN COOPER.

02:20.140 --> 02:21.850
WAIT. I THOUGHT HIS NAME

02:20.140 --> 02:21.850
WAS D.B. COOPER.

02:21.850 --> 02:23.602
THAT WAS MISHEARD

02:21.850 --> 02:23.602
BY A REPORTER AT THE SCENE,

02:23.602 --> 02:25.395
AND THEN IT WAS REPEATED

02:23.602 --> 02:25.395
UNTIL IT BECAME GOSPEL.

02:25.395 --> 02:27.022
I'M SORRY. I DIDN'T MEAN

02:25.395 --> 02:27.022
TO INTERRUPT YOUR SWOONING.

02:27.022 --> 02:28.523
GO ON AND SWOON.

02:28.523 --> 02:31.485
HE SHOWS THE STEWARDESS

02:28.523 --> 02:31.485
WHAT APPEARS TO BE A BOMB.

02:31.485 --> 02:34.362
HE DEMANDS $200,000 IN CASH

02:31.485 --> 02:34.362
AND FOUR PARACHUTES.

02:34.362 --> 02:36.824
HE GETS THEM. THEN HE

02:34.362 --> 02:36.824
DOES SOMETHING NO ONE EXPECTS.

02:36.824 --> 02:38.033
SOMEWHERE OVER THE CASCADES,

02:38.033 --> 02:39.743
WHICH IS NEAR

02:38.033 --> 02:39.743
TO WHERE WE ARE NOW,

02:39.743 --> 02:44.581
HE JUMPS, AND HE JUST --

02:39.743 --> 02:44.581
HE DISAPPEARS FOREVER.

02:44.581 --> 02:46.333
SOPHIE, JUST REAL QUICK --

02:46.333 --> 02:50.087
YOU HAD A POSTER OF D.B. OVER

02:46.333 --> 02:50.087
YOUR BED WHEN YOU WAS, LIKE, 15.

02:50.087 --> 02:51.713
-TELL THE TRUTH --

02:50.087 --> 02:51.713
YOU DID, DIDN'T YOU?

02:50.087 --> 02:51.713
-SO WHAT? WHAT IF I DID?

02:51.713 --> 02:53.674
WAIT. LET ME SAVE US

02:51.713 --> 02:53.674
A LITTLE TROUBLE HERE, OKAY?

02:53.674 --> 02:55.383
THE GUY JUMPED

02:53.674 --> 02:55.383
FROM 10,000 FEET, YEAH,

02:55.383 --> 02:56.677
BUT IT WAS SEVEN BELOW ZERO.

02:56.677 --> 02:58.095
HE'S IN A 1971 PARACHUTE.

02:58.095 --> 03:00.514
HE JUMPED IN BAD WEATHER

02:58.095 --> 03:00.514
OVER DENSE WOODS.

03:00.514 --> 03:02.641
HE DIDN'T SURVIVE. CASE CLOSED.

03:02.641 --> 03:06.145
ALL RIGHT, THIS IS -- THIS IS

03:02.641 --> 03:06.145
PROBABLY JUST A, YOU KNOW,

03:02.641 --> 03:06.145
A WASTE OF TIME.

03:06.145 --> 03:10.524
-WHAT?!

03:06.145 --> 03:10.524
-BUT I PROMISED

03:06.145 --> 03:10.524
THAT WE WOULD TRY.

03:10.524 --> 03:13.902
SO, I'M GONNA GO TALK

03:10.524 --> 03:13.902
TO McSWEETEN'S DAD,

03:13.902 --> 03:16.195
AND, HARDISON, YOU'RE GONNA

03:13.902 --> 03:16.195
FOLLOW UP ON THE OLD CASE FILE.

03:16.195 --> 03:18.157
THE OLD CASE FILE

03:16.195 --> 03:18.157
THAT PARKER STOLE?

03:18.157 --> 03:20.659
-YEAH.

03:18.157 --> 03:20.659
-THE ONE THAT'S, LIKE,

03:18.157 --> 03:20.659
80 VOLUMES LONG?

03:20.659 --> 03:24.121
-[ LAUGHS ]

03:20.659 --> 03:24.121
-DON'T WORRY.

03:20.659 --> 03:24.121
I GOT YOU SOME HELP.

03:27.958 --> 03:28.959
MR. REYNOLDS.

03:28.959 --> 03:30.502
SPECIAL AGENT THOMAS?

03:30.502 --> 03:33.755
YOU CAN CALL ME ALAN.

03:30.502 --> 03:33.755
THIS ISN'T A BUREAU MATTER.

03:33.755 --> 03:35.340
CALL ME STEVE.

03:35.340 --> 03:36.967
I WAS PETER McSWEETEN'S PARTNER

03:35.340 --> 03:36.967
ON THE COOPER CASE.

03:36.967 --> 03:38.552
MM.

03:38.552 --> 03:41.847
WELL, WE'RE GONNA BE WORKING

03:38.552 --> 03:41.847
WITH MR. DALWORTH HERE.

03:41.847 --> 03:44.183
HE'S A PRIVATE CONSULTANT.

03:44.183 --> 03:46.226
WELL...ANYTHING FOR PETER,

03:44.183 --> 03:46.226
BUT, UH,

03:46.226 --> 03:49.521
YOU SHOULD KNOW

03:46.226 --> 03:49.521
THIS WASN'T JUST A CASE FOR ME.

03:49.521 --> 03:50.981
IT WAS PERSONAL.

03:50.981 --> 03:53.859
MY, UM, LATE WIFE

03:50.981 --> 03:53.859
WAS A STEWARDESS ON THE PLANE.

03:53.859 --> 03:55.152
OH. WOW.

03:55.152 --> 03:56.945
WELL, THEN,

03:55.152 --> 03:56.945
YOU'RE THE RIGHT MAN TO ASK.

03:56.945 --> 03:58.655
IT SEEMS EVERYONE HAS A THEORY

03:56.945 --> 03:58.655
ABOUT COOPER. WHAT'S YOURS?

03:58.655 --> 04:01.992
ABOUT A YEAR

03:58.655 --> 04:01.992
AFTER COOPER VANISHED,

04:01.992 --> 04:05.996
RICHARD McCOY HIJACKS A PLANE

04:01.992 --> 04:05.996
OUT OF DENVER,

04:05.996 --> 04:07.789
GETS CAUGHT,

04:05.996 --> 04:07.789
SENTENCED TO 45 YEARS.

04:07.789 --> 04:11.126
SOME TIME LATER, HE MAKES A GUN

04:07.789 --> 04:11.126
OUT OF DENTAL PASTE

04:11.126 --> 04:14.088
AND BREAKS THROUGH THE

04:11.126 --> 04:14.088
PRISON GATES IN A GARBAGE TRUCK.

04:14.088 --> 04:16.673
DIES IN A GUNFIGHT WITH THE FBI.

04:16.673 --> 04:20.135
THERE'S A FELLA IN FLORIDA,

04:16.673 --> 04:20.135
A DUANE WEBER,

04:20.135 --> 04:23.180
ADMITTED TO BEING COOPER

04:20.135 --> 04:23.180
ON HIS DEATH BED IN 1995.

04:23.180 --> 04:26.600
YOU WANT A THEORY?

04:23.180 --> 04:26.600
TAKE YOUR PICK.

04:29.770 --> 04:31.479
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

04:31.479 --> 04:33.899
DAD?

04:31.479 --> 04:33.899
IS IT A GOOD TIME?

04:33.899 --> 04:37.903
[ SIGHS ] THE SIRENS ARE LURING

04:33.899 --> 04:37.903
THE SAILORS TO THEIR DEATH.

04:37.903 --> 04:41.489
LUCKILY, I KNOW HOW IT ENDS.

04:41.489 --> 04:42.991
I'LL BE BACK IN A FEW HOURS.

04:42.991 --> 04:44.451
TALLY HO, SON.

04:44.451 --> 04:46.536
UH...

04:46.536 --> 04:47.662
PETER McSWEETEN.

04:47.662 --> 04:48.789
NICK DALWORTH.

04:48.789 --> 04:51.125
-HAVE A SEAT.

04:48.789 --> 04:51.125
-THANK YOU.

04:51.125 --> 04:55.045
SO, YOU'RE A PROFILER

04:51.125 --> 04:55.045
WHO'S COME TO TAKE A RUN

04:55.045 --> 04:56.713
AT THE COOPER CASE.

04:56.713 --> 04:58.173
IF IT'S ALL RIGHT.

04:58.173 --> 05:02.928
I SPENT 40 YEARS TRYING

04:58.173 --> 05:02.928
TO UNDERSTAND ONE MAN.

05:02.928 --> 05:06.932
WHAT'S IT LIKE TO CLIMB

05:02.928 --> 05:06.932
INTO THE MIND

05:06.932 --> 05:08.767
OF A DIFFERENT CRIMINAL

05:06.932 --> 05:08.767
EVERY DAY?

05:08.767 --> 05:11.979
WELL, IF I TOLD YOU I LEFT IT

05:08.767 --> 05:11.979
AT THE OFFICE, I'D BE LYING.

05:11.979 --> 05:15.732
THEN THIS IS A STORY

05:11.979 --> 05:15.732
YOU SHOULD HEAR.

05:15.732 --> 05:19.861
IT BEGAN THE DAY BEFORE

05:15.732 --> 05:19.861
THANKSGIVING, 1971.

05:19.861 --> 05:22.239
[ SIGHS ]

05:22.239 --> 05:23.824
[  SPEAKING INDISTINCTLY  ]

05:23.824 --> 05:25.075
OH, WHAT'S THAT?

05:25.075 --> 05:27.077
JUST A LITTLE SOMETHING

05:25.075 --> 05:27.077
FOR THE NEW JOB.

05:27.077 --> 05:28.078
[ CHUCKLES ]

05:28.078 --> 05:29.204
WELL!

05:31.957 --> 05:33.541
THIS IS GONNA BE TOUGH.

05:33.541 --> 05:36.753
SAYING GOODBYE TO THE PEOPLE

05:33.541 --> 05:36.753
YOU CARE ABOUT ALWAYS IS.

05:40.715 --> 05:42.968
-TALLY HO, TODD.

05:40.715 --> 05:42.968
-TALLY HO, DAD.

05:44.469 --> 05:47.722
IT WAS MY FIRST DAY

05:44.469 --> 05:47.722
AS CHIEF OF THE SEATTLE OFFICE.

05:47.722 --> 05:50.433
BEFORE I REPORTED THERE,

05:47.722 --> 05:50.433
I HAD TO DO ONE THING --

05:50.433 --> 05:53.145
THANK THE PEOPLE I SERVED WITH

05:50.433 --> 05:53.145
HERE IN PORTLAND.

05:53.145 --> 05:55.396
HAIL, HAIL.

05:53.145 --> 05:55.396
THE CONQUERING HERO RETURNS.

05:55.396 --> 05:56.898
I JUST CAME TO SAY GOODBYE.

05:56.898 --> 05:58.441
YOU WERE A GREAT PARTNER,

05:56.898 --> 05:58.441
REGGIE,

05:58.441 --> 05:59.818
AND YOU GOT A BRIGHT FUTURE

05:58.441 --> 05:59.818
HERE AT THE BUREAU.

05:59.818 --> 06:01.444
ESPECIALLY NOW

05:59.818 --> 06:01.444
THAT YOU'RE MOVING ON.

06:01.444 --> 06:03.280
YOU WAS, UH, KIND OF

06:01.444 --> 06:03.280
PINNING MY WINGS BACK, CHIEF.

06:03.280 --> 06:05.115
-NO OFFENSE.

06:03.280 --> 06:05.115
-NONE TAKEN.

06:05.115 --> 06:08.409
IF I COULD JUST GET EVERYONE'S

06:05.115 --> 06:08.409
ATTENTION FOR -- FOR A SECOND.

06:10.537 --> 06:11.955
[ SIGHS ]

06:11.955 --> 06:14.582
SO, OUR MOTTO IS

06:11.955 --> 06:14.582
"FIDELITY, BRAVERY, INTEGRITY."

06:14.582 --> 06:17.169
AND ALL MY TIME HERE

06:14.582 --> 06:17.169
IN PORTLAND, I MUST SAY

06:17.169 --> 06:19.213
YOU HAVE ALL SHOWN THOSE

06:17.169 --> 06:19.213
QUALITIES EVERY SINGLE DAY,

06:19.213 --> 06:20.630
AND FOR THAT, I THANK YOU.

06:20.630 --> 06:25.344
BUT IF I COULD DO ONE THING

06:20.630 --> 06:25.344
BEFORE I LEAVE,

06:25.344 --> 06:27.762
I'D LIKE TO ADD A WORD

06:25.344 --> 06:27.762
TO THAT SIGN --

06:27.762 --> 06:28.847
"COMPASSION."

06:28.847 --> 06:30.598
NEVER FORGET

06:28.847 --> 06:30.598
TO PUT YOURSELVES

06:30.598 --> 06:32.809
IN THE SHOES

06:30.598 --> 06:32.809
OF THE PEOPLE WE SERVE,

06:32.809 --> 06:36.021
AND NOT JUST THE VICTIMS,

06:32.809 --> 06:36.021
BUT THE PERPETRATORS AS WELL.

06:36.021 --> 06:38.315
THEY'RE ALL

06:36.021 --> 06:38.315
DESERVING OF OUR MERCY.

06:38.315 --> 06:40.192
THANK YOU.

06:40.192 --> 06:42.527
[ APPLAUSE ]

06:44.403 --> 06:45.947
THERE YOU ARE.

06:45.947 --> 06:49.201
-MA'AM, YOUR DRINK.

06:45.947 --> 06:49.201
-THANK YOU.

