[ CHUCKLES ]

07:09.512 --> 07:11.639
DON'T KNOCK IT TILL YOU TRY IT.

07:11.639 --> 07:14.059
[ SCOFFS ]

07:11.639 --> 07:14.059
NOT EVEN THIS STOPS THEM!

07:14.059 --> 07:15.269
I WANT COMBAT PAY.

07:15.269 --> 07:17.729
WELL, STEPHANIE,

07:15.269 --> 07:17.729
GOOD LUCK WITH THAT.

07:17.729 --> 07:18.897
[ LAUGHS ]

07:24.736 --> 07:28.407
WELCOME TO FLIGHT 305.

