WHAT CAN I GET FOR YOU, SIR?

07:28.407 --> 07:30.533
BOURBON AND WATER, PLEASE.

07:30.533 --> 07:32.035
AND THIS IS FOR YOU.

07:32.035 --> 07:33.578
[ CHUCKLES ]

07:38.166 --> 07:41.336
WHAT DID I TELL YOU?

07:38.166 --> 07:41.336
ANOTHER LOVESICK BUSINESSMAN.

07:41.336 --> 07:43.463
NOW, NOW. DON'T BE SO HASTY.

07:45.590 --> 07:46.967
[ BOTH CHUCKLE ]

07:46.967 --> 07:49.636
ONCE COOPER HANDED

07:46.967 --> 07:49.636
STEPHANIE RITTER THE NOTE,

07:49.636 --> 07:51.721
SHE BECAME

07:49.636 --> 07:51.721
HIS CONNECTION TO US.

