20:31.731 --> 20:35.818
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

20:35.818 --> 20:37.277
[ BEEPS ]

20:35.818 --> 20:37.277
YEAH?

20:37.277 --> 20:39.864
NATE, I FOUND DANIEL COOPER.

20:39.864 --> 20:41.741
LOOKS LIKE HE DIED IN 1968,

20:41.741 --> 20:44.368
THREE YEARS

20:41.741 --> 20:44.368
BEFORE THE HIJACKING.

20:44.368 --> 20:45.452
IT'S ANOTHER DEAD END.

20:45.452 --> 20:47.997
COOPER DIED ABROAD -- VIETNAM.

20:47.997 --> 20:50.041
THAT'S WHY HARDISON

20:47.997 --> 20:50.041
DIDN'T FIND A DEATH CERTIFICATE.

20:50.041 --> 20:52.877
ANYWAY, IT WAS THREE YEARS

20:50.041 --> 20:52.877
BEFORE THE HIJACKING.

20:52.877 --> 20:55.088
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

20:55.088 --> 20:57.090
[ Speed-dialing ]

20:57.090 --> 20:58.382
YEAH, HARDISON.

20:58.382 --> 21:00.009
What else did you find

20:58.382 --> 21:00.009
in the case file?

21:00.009 --> 21:01.969
IT'S NOT WHAT'S IN HERE.

21:00.009 --> 21:01.969
IT'S WHAT'S MISSING.

21:01.969 --> 21:04.597
THERE'S NO DNA EVIDENCE,

21:01.969 --> 21:04.597
EVEN THOUGH THEY PULLED

21:01.969 --> 21:04.597
HAIRS AND FIBERS

21:04.597 --> 21:07.349
FROM THE HIJACKER'S CLOTHING.

21:07.349 --> 21:09.476
YOU KNOW, I RETIRED BEFORE

21:07.349 --> 21:09.476
THAT STUFF BECAME IMPORTANT,

21:09.476 --> 21:10.978
BUT I KNOW WHERE

21:09.476 --> 21:10.978
IT MUST BE STORED.

21:10.978 --> 21:12.813
THE CRIME LAB.

21:12.813 --> 21:15.357
DNA file's secure.

21:12.813 --> 21:15.357
On my way.

21:15.357 --> 21:16.859
COPY.

21:16.859 --> 21:19.570
[ CHUCKLES ]

21:16.859 --> 21:19.570
LOOK AT ALL THIS STUFF.

21:19.570 --> 21:22.031
I asked the Bureau

21:19.570 --> 21:22.031
for a desk lamp six months ago.

21:22.031 --> 21:24.324
IS THAT A CROSSBOW?

21:22.031 --> 21:24.324
[ VEHICLE DOOR OPENS ]

21:24.324 --> 21:25.576
HERE!

21:26.326 --> 21:27.327
COME ON!

21:27.327 --> 21:28.621
LET'S GO, LET'S GO, LET'S GO!

21:28.621 --> 21:31.498
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

21:31.498 --> 21:33.667
PETER,

21:31.498 --> 21:33.667
ANY REGRETS ABOUT THE CASE?

21:33.667 --> 21:34.752
JUST ONE.

21:34.752 --> 21:36.336
MY BOY, TODD, HAD A HARD TIME

21:36.336 --> 21:38.589
GROWING UP

21:36.336 --> 21:38.589
IN THE SHADOW OF D.B. COOPER.

21:38.589 --> 21:40.424
[ TELEPHONE RINGS ]

21:38.589 --> 21:40.424
McSWEETEN.

21:40.424 --> 21:41.842
THANK YOU.

21:41.842 --> 21:44.470
MICHAEL NOVAK'S HERE.

21:44.470 --> 21:46.180
EIGHT YEARS AFTER THE HIJACKING,

21:46.180 --> 21:49.267
AND NOW THIS KID THINKS THEY GOT

21:46.180 --> 21:49.267
THE COMPOSITE SKETCH WRONG?

21:49.267 --> 21:51.102
WELL, HIM,

21:49.267 --> 21:51.102
HE WAS ON THE PLANE,

21:51.102 --> 21:53.395
AND HE SWEARS THAT COOPER LOOKED

21:51.102 --> 21:53.395
DIFFERENT THAN IN THE SKETCH.

21:53.395 --> 21:54.480
COME ON. WE HAVE TO --

21:54.480 --> 21:55.940
FOLLOW EVERY LEAD.

21:54.480 --> 21:55.940
ALL RIGHT.

21:55.940 --> 21:57.483
[ TELEPHONE RINGS ]

21:57.483 --> 21:58.651
McSWEETEN.

21:58.651 --> 21:59.652
TODD?

21:59.652 --> 22:01.237
TALLY HO, SON.

22:01.237 --> 22:03.363
WHERE -- WHERE ARE YOU?

22:03.363 --> 22:06.450
YEAH, OKAY.

22:03.363 --> 22:06.450
I'LL BE -- I'LL BE RIGHT THERE.

22:06.450 --> 22:07.827
I --

22:07.827 --> 22:10.288
GO. GO.

22:07.827 --> 22:10.288
I GOT THE NOVAK INTERVIEW.

22:12.081 --> 22:14.125
[ HORN HONKS ]

22:23.634 --> 22:24.885
WHAT HAPPENED?

22:24.885 --> 22:26.512
A BUNCH OF KIDS SAID

22:26.512 --> 22:29.640
THEY NEEDED TO BORROW MY BIKE

22:26.512 --> 22:29.640
TO LOOK FOR A LOST DOG.

22:29.640 --> 22:31.809
THEY SAID THEY'D BE RIGHT BACK.

22:31.809 --> 22:33.519
WHEN WAS THAT?

22:33.519 --> 22:35.313
THREE HOURS AGO.

22:35.313 --> 22:38.398
WHY DOES THIS

22:35.313 --> 22:38.398
KEEP HAPPENING TO ME?

22:38.398 --> 22:39.942
[ SIGHS ]

22:39.942 --> 22:44.113
EVERY DAY, I GO AND CHASE

22:39.942 --> 22:44.113
BAD GUYS -- SOME REALLY BAD.

22:44.113 --> 22:47.325
AND PRETTY SOON, YOU START

22:44.113 --> 22:47.325
TO SEE EVERYONE LIKE THAT.

22:47.325 --> 22:48.742
IT'S EASIER THAT WAY.

22:48.742 --> 22:51.204
NOW, YOU COULD --

22:48.742 --> 22:51.204
YOU COULD BE LIKE THAT, TOO.

22:51.204 --> 22:53.206
YOU WOULDN'T LOSE AS MANY BIKES.

22:53.206 --> 22:56.458
BUT I WON'T FIND ANY LOST DOGS.

22:56.458 --> 22:59.377
THAT'S RIGHT.

22:59.377 --> 23:01.005
[ SIGHS ]

23:01.005 --> 23:06.093
IT'S NOT A WEAKNESS TO SEE

23:01.005 --> 23:06.093
THE GOOD IN PEOPLE, ALL RIGHT?

23:06.093 --> 23:11.349
IT'S NOT A -- A FLAW

23:06.093 --> 23:11.349
OR A BAD THING TO -- TO TRUST.

23:11.349 --> 23:14.227
DO YOU WANT TO KNOW THE TRUTH,

23:11.349 --> 23:14.227
TODD?

23:14.227 --> 23:16.687
YOU'RE THE BEST GUY I KNOW.

23:17.604 --> 23:18.522
GET IN.

23:18.522 --> 23:20.358
I STILL BELIEVE THAT.

23:20.358 --> 23:23.236
THE PEOPLE I ARRESTED --

23:20.358 --> 23:23.236
THEY WERE HUMAN BEINGS TO ME.

23:23.236 --> 23:25.403
SOMETHING DROVE THEM

23:23.236 --> 23:25.403
TO CROSS THE LINE,

23:25.403 --> 23:28.241
BUT I ALWAYS BELIEVED

23:25.403 --> 23:28.241
THAT THEY COULD BE REDEEMED,

23:28.241 --> 23:29.742
EVEN COOPER.

23:29.742 --> 23:30.701
WOW.

23:30.701 --> 23:32.036
DON'T YOU BELIEVE THAT?

23:32.036 --> 23:34.621
NO. NO.

23:34.621 --> 23:36.165
I WISH I DID.

23:36.165 --> 23:38.084
THEN YOU CAN SEE

23:36.165 --> 23:38.084
WHY I'M WORRIED ABOUT MY SON.

23:38.084 --> 23:39.793
SURE.

23:39.793 --> 23:42.755
YOU'RE AFRAID OF WHAT THE HUNT

23:39.793 --> 23:42.755
FOR COOPER MIGHT DO TO HIM.

23:42.755 --> 23:45.632
I TRIED TO STOP HIM,

23:42.755 --> 23:45.632
BUT I SUPPOSE

23:45.632 --> 23:49.469
A SON WILL ALWAYS TRY TO AVENGE

23:45.632 --> 23:49.469
HIS FATHER'S DEFEATS.

23:49.469 --> 23:52.056
LIKE TELEMACHUS AND ODYSSEUS.

23:52.056 --> 23:53.266
[ CHUCKLES ]

23:53.266 --> 23:58.520
YOU DON'T HAVE TO FIND

23:53.266 --> 23:58.520
D.B. COOPER.

23:58.520 --> 24:00.898
HE'S...LOST SOMEWHERE

23:58.520 --> 24:00.898
IN THE DARKNESS.

24:00.898 --> 24:02.358
JUST...

24:02.358 --> 24:05.903
JUST MAKE SURE MY SON

24:02.358 --> 24:05.903
DOESN'T FOLLOW HIM THERE.

24:07.947 --> 24:10.991
WELL, IT'S GETTING LATE.

24:10.991 --> 24:12.034
UNTIL TOMORROW.

24:12.034 --> 24:14.120
I'LL BE HERE.

24:14.120 --> 24:15.329
THANK YOU.

24:15.329 --> 24:16.622
YEP.

24:24.255 --> 24:26.382
HEY. WHAT'S IN THE DNA FILE?

24:26.382 --> 24:28.301
THE DNA NEVER MADE IT

24:26.382 --> 24:28.301
TO THE MAIN CASE FILE

24:28.301 --> 24:30.428
BECAUSE IT WAS CONTAMINATED

24:28.301 --> 24:30.428
BY THE INVESTIGATING TEAM.

24:30.428 --> 24:31.929
EVERYBODY'S DNA IS IN THERE --

24:31.929 --> 24:34.181
COOPER'S, REYNOLDS',

24:31.929 --> 24:34.181
McSWEETEN'S, THE LAB TECHS'.

24:34.181 --> 24:35.557
YEAH, I WAS AFRAID OF THAT.

24:35.557 --> 24:36.934
THAT'S WHAT HAPPENS

24:35.557 --> 24:36.934
SOMETIMES WITH OLD CASES

24:36.934 --> 24:38.269
WHEN THEY PREDATE

24:36.934 --> 24:38.269
MODERN FORENSICS.

24:38.269 --> 24:39.645
SO, WHAT?

24:38.269 --> 24:39.645
BACK TO SQUARE ONE?

24:39.645 --> 24:41.563
NO, I PREFER

24:39.645 --> 24:41.563
BACK TO THE DRAWING BOARD.

24:41.563 --> 24:42.648
IT'S MORE HOPEFUL.

24:42.648 --> 24:44.108
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

24:44.108 --> 24:45.359
IT'S McSWEETEN.

24:45.359 --> 24:46.902
HI.

24:48.279 --> 24:50.114
HEY --

24:52.741 --> 24:54.576
YEAH. I'M SORRY.

24:54.576 --> 24:56.287
OKAY.

24:56.287 --> 24:58.164
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

24:58.164 --> 25:01.459
HIS DAD DIED LAST NIGHT.

25:01.459 --> 25:03.877
[ SIGHS ]

25:03.877 --> 25:07.089
WE SHOULD BE DRINKING COFFEE.

25:09.507 --> 25:12.052
DAD LOVED HIS COFFEE.

25:09.507 --> 25:12.052
[ CHUCKLES ]

25:12.052 --> 25:16.182
YEAH. HE'D LET IT GET ICE COLD

25:12.052 --> 25:16.182
AND TOP IT OFF ALL DAY LONG.

25:16.182 --> 25:18.476
[ LAUGHS ]

25:16.182 --> 25:18.476
DROVE ME CRAZY.

25:18.476 --> 25:20.686
WHAT ELSE

25:18.476 --> 25:20.686
DO YOU REMEMBER ABOUT HIM?

25:20.686 --> 25:23.063
WELL, HE WAS A HELL OF A SHOT.

25:23.063 --> 25:25.107
YEAH, BUT A TERRIBLE DRIVER.

25:23.063 --> 25:25.107
[ CHUCKLES ]

25:25.107 --> 25:27.651
[ LAUGHS ]

25:25.107 --> 25:27.651
THAT'S TRUE.

25:27.651 --> 25:29.569
ONE TIME,

25:27.651 --> 25:29.569
WE'RE IN THIS HIGH-SPEED CHASE,

25:29.569 --> 25:31.905
AND HE PLOWS US RIGHT

25:29.569 --> 25:31.905
INTO THIS RESTAURANT DUMPSTER.

25:31.905 --> 25:33.032
POW!

25:33.032 --> 25:34.992
WHAT A MESS!

25:34.992 --> 25:37.161
SO WE GET OUT OF THE CAR,

25:34.992 --> 25:37.161
WE'RE LOOKING AT THE DAMAGE,

25:37.161 --> 25:38.829
AND THIS GIRL

25:37.161 --> 25:38.829
COMES RUNNING UP TO US

25:38.829 --> 25:41.332
AND SAYS SOMEBODY ATTACKED HER

25:38.829 --> 25:41.332
AND THAT MAYBE

25:41.332 --> 25:44.418
SHE THOUGHT HE WAS WITH THE

25:41.332 --> 25:44.418
C.I.A. OR ONE OF THE RUSSIANS.

25:44.418 --> 25:47.254
SHE'S TRIPPING ON ACID.

25:44.418 --> 25:47.254
SHE'S A RUNAWAY.

25:47.254 --> 25:51.091
SO I'M READY TO HAND HER OVER

25:47.254 --> 25:51.091
TO THE PARAMEDICS.

25:51.091 --> 25:54.678
PETER'S GOT HER

25:51.091 --> 25:54.678
IN THE BACK SEAT OF THE CAR.

25:54.678 --> 25:56.889
"TAKE US TO HIM,"

25:54.678 --> 25:56.889
HE TELLS HER.

25:56.889 --> 25:59.808
WE FOUND THE GUY!

25:56.889 --> 25:59.808
HE'S IN THE BUS STATION!

25:59.808 --> 26:02.644
AND THE NEXT DAY,

25:59.808 --> 26:02.644
HE TAKES US TO THE WOODS

26:02.644 --> 26:05.439
WHERE HE'S BURIED

26:02.644 --> 26:05.439
THREE OTHER RUNAWAYS.

26:05.439 --> 26:07.274
I SAY TO PETER,

26:07.274 --> 26:09.860
"HEY. THIS GIRL, SHE WAS --

26:07.274 --> 26:09.860
SHE WAS STRUNG OUT.

26:09.860 --> 26:12.821
SHE WAS RANTING.

26:09.860 --> 26:12.821
I MEAN, HOW DID YOU KNOW?"

26:12.821 --> 26:18.202
HE SAID, "ALL I HEARD...

26:12.821 --> 26:18.202
WAS THAT SHE WAS AFRAID."

26:18.202 --> 26:19.786
MM.

26:19.786 --> 26:25.792
SO, HERE'S TO PETER McSWEETEN,

26:25.792 --> 26:27.253
WHO COULDN'T DRIVE A LICK.

26:32.383 --> 26:34.051
[ SIGHS ]

26:35.177 --> 26:37.763
I WANT TO THANK YOU AGAIN

26:35.177 --> 26:37.763
FOR TRYING.

26:40.307 --> 26:43.436
FROM NOW ON, THE HUNT

26:40.307 --> 26:43.436
FOR D.B. COOPER IS ON ME.

26:53.695 --> 26:56.073
[ SIGHS ]

26:56.073 --> 26:57.783
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

26:59.243 --> 27:01.078
WORKING.

27:06.750 --> 27:09.795
YOU HEAR WHAT McSWEETEN SAID

27:06.750 --> 27:09.795
BACK THERE?

27:09.795 --> 27:12.005
THIS WAS GONNA BE HIS FIGHT NOW?

27:21.014 --> 27:23.434
I'M NOT GONNA LET THAT HAPPEN.

27:23.434 --> 27:25.852
MICHAEL NOVAK WAS A 10-YEAR-OLD

27:23.434 --> 27:25.852
PASSENGER ON THE PLANE

27:25.852 --> 27:27.938
WHEN HE TOLD STEVE REYNOLDS

27:25.852 --> 27:27.938
THAT D.B. COOPER

27:27.938 --> 27:29.440
LOOKED DIFFERENT

27:27.938 --> 27:29.440
THAN THE SKETCH.

27:29.440 --> 27:32.234
YEAH, BUT HE ONLY REMEMBERED

27:29.440 --> 27:32.234
AFTER EIGHT YEARS.

27:32.234 --> 27:34.236
AND HE SAW HIM FOR ALL OF,

27:32.234 --> 27:34.236
WHAT, 10 SECONDS?

27:34.236 --> 27:35.946
THE STEWARDESS --

27:34.236 --> 27:35.946
SHE WAS ON THE FLIGHT,

27:35.946 --> 27:38.031
SITTING NEXT TO HIM

27:35.946 --> 27:38.031
FOR FIVE HOURS STRAIGHT.

27:38.031 --> 27:39.908
SHE STUDIED

27:38.031 --> 27:39.908
EVERY INCH OF HIS FACE.

27:39.908 --> 27:41.701
WHAT DO WE KNOW

27:39.908 --> 27:41.701
ABOUT THIS CASE?

27:41.827 --> 27:44.163
WHAT DO WE KNOW

27:41.827 --> 27:44.163
ABOUT THIS CASE?

27:44.163 --> 27:45.289
I MEAN, WE DON'T HAVE A SUSPECT.

27:45.289 --> 27:46.832
WE HAVE HUNDREDS OF SUSPECTS.

27:46.832 --> 27:49.209
WE DON'T EVEN KNOW

27:46.832 --> 27:49.209
IF HE SURVIVED THE JUMP, RIGHT?

27:49.209 --> 27:51.337
THE ONLY THING

27:49.209 --> 27:51.337
THAT WE HAVE FOR CERTAIN --

27:51.337 --> 27:53.088
WE HAVE THIS SKETCH.

27:53.088 --> 27:55.090
THIS SKETCH THAT WAS PROVIDED

27:53.088 --> 27:55.090
BY THE STEWARDESS'S DESCRIPTION.

27:55.090 --> 27:58.469
THAT'S THE ONLY THING

27:55.090 --> 27:58.469
THAT NO ONE HAS EVER QUESTIONED.

28:07.894 --> 28:10.606
WHERE WAS THE STEWARDESS SITTING

28:07.894 --> 28:10.606
WHEN THE FBI INTERVIEWED HER?

28:10.606 --> 28:12.525
ON THE PLANE. WHY?

28:12.525 --> 28:14.818
AND WHAT WAS

28:12.525 --> 28:14.818
THE IN-FLIGHT MAGAZINE?

28:16.529 --> 28:18.822
SKY CLASS.

28:18.822 --> 28:20.782
SHOW ME THE BACK COVER.

28:23.202 --> 28:24.786
ENLARGE.

28:26.246 --> 28:27.665
SKETCH.

28:31.877 --> 28:35.172
NOW, WHY WOULD SHE LIE?

28:48.768 --> 28:50.854
[ DOORBELL RINGS ]

28:52.690 --> 28:54.525
-NICK! HEY!

28:52.690 --> 28:54.525
-STEVE.

28:54.525 --> 28:55.901
HEY, SORRY TO BOTHER YOU.

28:55.901 --> 28:57.528
COME ON IN.

28:55.901 --> 28:57.528
IT'S ALL RIGHT.

28:57.528 --> 28:59.112
I WAS IN THE NEIGHBORHOOD,

28:59.112 --> 29:01.532
AND I JUST HAD A COUPLE

28:59.112 --> 29:01.532
OF QUESTIONS ABOUT THE CASE

29:01.532 --> 29:03.283
I WANTED TO RUN BY YOU.

29:03.283 --> 29:04.451
I HOPE IT'S ALL RIGHT.

29:04.451 --> 29:05.869
YEAH.

29:05.869 --> 29:07.829
OH, HERE'S...STEPHANIE?

29:07.829 --> 29:10.165
WOW.

29:10.165 --> 29:11.458
SHE SURE WAS BEAUTIFUL.

29:11.458 --> 29:14.294
YEAH. MISS HER EVERY DAY.

29:14.294 --> 29:16.880
SHE'S BEEN GONE 10 YEARS NOW.

29:16.880 --> 29:17.881
10 YEARS NOW?

29:17.881 --> 29:19.091
[ KETTLE WHISTLES ]

29:19.091 --> 29:22.219
AH. JUST MAKING SOME TEA.

29:19.091 --> 29:22.219
EXCUSE ME.

29:27.933 --> 29:31.186
YOU AND HER

29:27.933 --> 29:31.186
GOT MARRIED IN 1972, RIGHT?

29:40.237 --> 29:42.030
UNCLE STEVE?

29:47.369 --> 29:50.205
NOW WHY DON'T YOU TELL US

29:47.369 --> 29:50.205
THE REAL STORY OF D.B. COOPER?

29:52.541 --> 29:58.130
I'VE BEEN CARRYING THIS AROUND

29:52.541 --> 29:58.130
WITH ME FOR A LONG TIME.

29:58.130 --> 30:02.175
WELCOME TO FLIGHT 305.

29:58.130 --> 30:02.175
WHAT CAN I GET FOR YOU, SIR?

30:02.175 --> 30:06.096
I BELIEVE I'LL HAVE

30:02.175 --> 30:06.096
A BOURBON AND WATER, PLEASE.

30:06.096 --> 30:08.599
AND THIS IS FOR YOU.

30:08.599 --> 30:10.309
[ CHUCKLES ]

30:10.309 --> 30:12.018
ARE YOU SCARED?

30:13.687 --> 30:16.189
DO YOU THINK I'M CRAZY?

30:26.659 --> 30:28.327
WHAT ABOUT NOW?

30:29.911 --> 30:32.038
I'M NOT DOING THIS

30:29.911 --> 30:32.038
'CAUSE I WANT TO.

30:32.038 --> 30:34.249
I'M DOING IT

30:32.038 --> 30:34.249
BECAUSE I MADE A PROMISE.

30:34.249 --> 30:35.375
TO WHO?

30:35.375 --> 30:38.044
[ METAL JINGLING ]

30:38.878 --> 30:41.173
P.F.C. DANIEL COOPER.

30:41.173 --> 30:43.842
I HELD HIS HAND WHEN HE DIED.

30:43.842 --> 30:48.597
AND I TOLD HIM THAT I WAS GONNA

30:43.842 --> 30:48.597
TAKE CARE OF HIS FAMILY,

30:48.597 --> 30:50.557
AND THAT'S WHAT I'M GOING TO DO.

30:52.058 --> 30:54.060
PLEASE, I DON'T WANT TO DIE.

30:54.060 --> 30:56.313
THIS -- THIS RING?

30:56.313 --> 31:00.025
IT'S JUST FOR SHOW

30:56.313 --> 31:00.025
TO KEEP THE DRUNKS AWAY.

31:00.025 --> 31:01.901
BUT I WANT TO GET MARRIED,

31:00.025 --> 31:01.901
AND I WANT TO HAVE KIDS.

31:01.901 --> 31:04.655
HEY. I'M NOT GONNA HURT YOU.

31:04.655 --> 31:05.864
OR ANYONE.

31:07.366 --> 31:09.284
DO YOU BELIEVE ME?

31:19.252 --> 31:20.754
WHAT DO YOU WANT ME TO DO?

31:24.508 --> 31:26.885
I THINK I'LL HAVE

31:24.508 --> 31:26.885
ANOTHER BOURBON AND WATER.

31:26.885 --> 31:29.429
KEEP THE CHANGE.

31:29.429 --> 31:31.640
[ KNOCKING ]

31:29.429 --> 31:31.640
HEY.

31:31.640 --> 31:32.891
LET'S SEE.

31:32.891 --> 31:35.644
YOU TELL THEM

31:32.891 --> 31:35.644
IF THEY TRY ANYTHING,

31:35.644 --> 31:37.771
I WILL SET THIS BOMB OFF.

31:41.441 --> 31:43.193
TELL THEM.

31:51.993 --> 31:54.663
[ RADIO CHATTER ]

31:55.497 --> 31:57.999
[ RATTLING ]

31:57.999 --> 31:59.793
WHAT WAS THAT?

31:57.999 --> 31:59.793
[ ALARM BLARING ]

31:59.793 --> 32:01.503
SOMETHING HAPPENED IN THE CABIN.

32:01.503 --> 32:03.547
LOOKS LIKE THE AFT DOOR IS OPEN.

32:05.591 --> 32:07.050
[ SIGHS ]

32:09.678 --> 32:11.805
DO NOT GO IN THERE!

32:11.805 --> 32:15.016
[ WIND HOWLING ]

32:19.438 --> 32:20.689
DON'T!

32:20.689 --> 32:21.690
STAY BACK!

32:21.690 --> 32:24.109
YOU'LL NEVER MAKE IT!

32:24.109 --> 32:25.944
THERE'S ONLY ONE WAY

32:24.109 --> 32:25.944
TO FIND OUT!

32:25.944 --> 32:29.072
LOOK, MAYBE IT SHOULD HAVE BEEN

32:25.944 --> 32:29.072
YOU INSTEAD OF YOUR FRIEND.

32:29.072 --> 32:31.324
BUT IT DOESN'T MATTER!

32:29.072 --> 32:31.324
[ SCREAMS ]

32:33.952 --> 32:35.370
DON'T DO THIS.

32:37.456 --> 32:39.499
