37:20.947 --> 37:23.575
THAN ANYTHING IN THE WORLD --

37:23.575 --> 37:25.451
TO BRING D.B. COOPER TO JUSTICE.

37:25.451 --> 37:27.412
YOU KNOW, TODD,

37:25.451 --> 37:27.412
YOUR -- YOUR DAD,

37:27.412 --> 37:31.624
HE HAD A GIFT THAT I BELIEVE

37:27.412 --> 37:31.624
HE PASSED ON TO YOU.

37:31.624 --> 37:34.627
HE COULD SEE GOODNESS

37:31.624 --> 37:34.627
IN PEOPLE.

37:34.627 --> 37:39.216
AND BECAUSE OF THAT, HE DID

37:34.627 --> 37:39.216
BRING D.B. COOPER TO JUSTICE.

37:57.442 --> 37:59.027
[ CAMERA SHUTTER CLICKS ]

37:59.027 --> 38:00.445
YOU KNOW, IT'S FAIR TO SAY

37:59.027 --> 38:00.445
THAT THE DAY

38:00.445 --> 38:03.907
THAT PETER McSWEETEN

38:00.445 --> 38:03.907
KNOCKED ON MY DOOR,

38:03.907 --> 38:05.951
